the college of graduate studies sends out a monthly newsletter email to graduate students and the greater campus community. these newsletters contain announcements about student, faculty, and alumni achievements, notifications about upcoming events and opportunities for students, as well as important information pertaining to scholarships, policies, graduation details and more. our newsletter runs in parallel with ourcgs blog, which houses spotlight articles and special features.if you are not currently receiving cgs monthly newsletter emails and would like to be added to our mailing list, please emailgraduate-studies@sjsu.eduwith the subject line "newsletter mailing list request."view 2020 newslettersview 2021 newslettersview 2022 newsletters